column1: i can wash dishes clean the floor and wipe glass surfaces using eco enzyme its a costeffective alternative compared to buying chemicalbased cleaning products from stores or supermarkets it removes stains that are usually difficult to clean on floors in kitchens on glass or on clothes it can be used as a cleaning agent it can be used to clean the floor with eco enzyme liquid it can be used to clean the house furniture and other household items it helps reduce the amount of organic waste in the surrounding environment it helps preserve the environment repels rats and serves as a dishwashing liquid it can be used as dish soap and floor cleaner it can clean glass and be used for washing dishes yes it can be turned into biogas animal feed and compost fertilizer yes it can be processed into organiccompost fertilizer animal feed handicrafts and biogas it can be processed into fertilizer organic waste can be turned into fertilizer yes it can be made into compost fertilizer and animal feed it can be turned into organic fertilizer organic fertilizer livestock feed handicrafts and many other products yes organic waste can be processed into more than just eco enzyme it can be used to make compost simple fertilizers and even animal feed yes for example it can be turned into compost
